Subject: [PATCH 4/4] feat: Add file save functionality for binary downloads
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add file_path parameter for /download endpoints automatically
- Save binary responses to local files to avoid MCP token limits
- Create directories recursively if they don't exist
- Provide fallback to Base64 if file_path not specified
- Test verified with receipt PDFs (42KB) and journal reports (286KB)

Resolves token limit issues where large binary responses
(49,214 tokens) exceeded Claude Code's 25,000 token limit.

